    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 MP</strong> to make a <strong>DC 10 Spell Check</strong> to heal a target within your Grove. </p><p><strong>Success:</strong> The target immediately regains <strong>1 HP</strong>. For the next minute, it regains an additional <strong>1 HP</strong> each time it ends its turn within your Grove. </p><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> They immediately regain <strong>+1 HP</strong>. </p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target only regains <strong>1 HP</strong> immediately.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Grove Enhancements</span></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Cure Sickness: (1 MP)</strong> You attempt to cure the target of a <strong>Poison</strong> or <strong>Disease</strong> afflicting it (your choice). Compare your <strong>Spell</strong> <strong>Check</strong> against the <strong>DC</strong> of the affliction. <br>Success: The <strong>Poison</strong> or <strong>Disease</strong> ends on the target.</p></li></ul>",
